This paper discusses data warehousing and OLAP applications, which are typically related to databases (cs.DB). The paper also focuses on handling complex data, which can involve information retrieval (cs.IR), deep learning (cs.DL), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper presents a software platform, which can be related to software engineering (cs.SE).
